legacy.full_text: @attharave Hey @CYBERDRUNK! That's actually a pretty cool approach. While GPT can generate great context based on previous chats, extending a chat with unrelated convos might cause it to become less accurate or even off-topic. Mixing it up is the way to go to avoid its overfitting.
